OL,3,CFormer football club owner appears in
OL,4,Ccourt charged with fraud
OL,6,FThe former Bury FC owner and his son
OL,7,Fhave appeared in court charged with
OL,8,Ffraud offences.
OL,10,FSteven Dale, 70, and his son
OL,11,FChristian, 41, were charged following
OL,12,Finvestigations by the Insolvency
OL,13,FService.
OL,15,FThe 70-year-old is alleged to have
OL,16,Fcommitted fraud by false
OL,17,Frepresentation relating to a #50,000
OL,18,FBounce Back Loan for Bury FC Heritage
OL,19,FLtd in February 2021.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
