OL,3,CFormer football club owner appears in
OL,4,Ccourt charged with fraud
OL,6,FDale, of Heath Rise, Whitmore,
OL,7,FStaffordshire, is also charged with
OL,8,Ffailing to keep, preserve or deliver
OL,9,Fup adequate accounting records under
OL,10,Fthe Companies Act 2006 and Insolvency
OL,11,FAct 1986 for The Bury Football Club
OL,12,FCompany Limited and Dale Acquisitions
OL,13,FLtd.
OL,15,FChristian, of the same address, is
OL,16,Fcharged with the same offences under
OL,17,Fthe Companies Act 2006 and Insolvency
OL,18,FAct 1986 in relation to Dale
OL,19,FAcquisitions Ltd.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
