PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774127152
OL,3,CFormer football club owner appears in
OL,4,Ccourt charged with fraud
OL,6,FBoth were bailed after appearing
OL,7,Fbefore Chester Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,F19 March.
OL,10,FThey will next appear before
OL,11,FManchester Minshull Street Crown Court
OL,12,Ffor a plea and trial preparation
OL,13,Fhearing on Thursday 16 April.
